// `rgbToRgb`
// Handle bounds / percentage checking to conform to CSS color spec
// <http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-color/>
// *Assumes:* r, g, b in [0, 255] or [0, 1]
// *Returns:* { r, g, b } in [0, 255]
